quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  26,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  26,1,toy seen meem
  26,2,yeh kitaab Mubin ki ayaat hain
  26,3,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, shayad tum is gham mein apni jaan kho do ge ke yeh log imaan nahi laatay"
  26,4,hum chahain to aasman se aisi nishani nazil kar satke hain ke inn ki gardanein is ke agay jhuk jayen
  26,5,inn logon ke paas Rehman ki taraf se jo nai nasiyaat bhi aati hai yeh is se mun mourr letay hain
  26,6,"ab ke yeh jhutla chuke hain, anqareeb inn ko is cheez ki haqeeqat ( mukhtalif tareeqon se ) maloom ho jaye gi jis ka yeh mazaq uratay rahay hain"
  26,7,aur kya unhon ne kabhi zameen par nigah nahi daali ke hum ne kitni kaseer miqdaar mein har terhan ki umdah nabataat is mein peda ki hain ?
  26,8,"yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar maan-ne walay nahi"
  26,9,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
  26,10,"aِnhin is waqt ka qissa sunaaoo jab ke tumahray rab ne moose ko puraka"" zalim qoum ke paas ja"
  26,11,"firaon ki qoum ke paas, kya woh drtay nahi? """
  26,12,"uss ne arz kya"" ae rab, mujhe khauf hai ke woh mujhe jhutla den ge"
  26,13,mera seenah ghat-ta hai aur meri zabaan nahi chalti aap haroon ki taraf risalat bhejen
  26,14,"aur mujh par unn ke haan aik jurm ka ilzaam bhi hai, is liye darta hon ke woh mujhe qatal kar den ge """
  26,15,"farmaya"" hargiz nahi, tum dono jao hamari nishanain le kar, hum tumahray sath sab kuch suntay rahen ge"
  26,16,"firaon ke paas jao aur is se kaho, hum ko Rab-ul-Aa'lmeen ne is liye bheja hai"
  26,17,"ke to bani Israel ko hamaray sath jaane day """
  26,18,"firaon ne kaha"" kya hum ne tujh ko apne haan bacha sa nahi paala tha? to ne apni Umar ke kayi saal hamaray haan guzaray"
  26,19,"aur is ke baad kar gaya jo kuch ke kar gaya, to bara ahsaan faramosh aadmi hai """
  26,20,"moose ne jawab diya"" uss waqt woh kaam mein ne nadanstgi mein kar diya tha"
  26,21,phir mein tumahray khauf se bhaag gaya is ke baad mere rab ne mujh ko hukum ataa kya aur mujhe Rasolo-n mein shaamil kar liya
  26,22,"raha tera ahsaan jo to ne mujh par jataayaa hai to is ki haqeeqat yeh hai ke to ne bani Israel ko ghulam bana liya tha """
  26,23,"firaon ne kaha"" aur yeh rab alameen kya hota hai? """
  26,24,"moose ne jawab diya"" aasman aur zameen ka rab, aur unn sab cheezon ka rab jo aasman aur zameen ke darmain hain, agar tum yaqeen laane walay ho """
  26,25,"firaon ne apne gird o paish ke logon se kaha"" suntay ho? """
  26,26,"moose ne kaha"" tumhara rab bhi aur tumahray un aaba o ajdaad ka rab bhi jo guzar chuke hain """
  26,27,"firaon ne ( hazreen se ) kaha"" tumahray yeh rasool sahib jo tumhari taraf beje gay hain, bilkul hi pagal maloom hotay hain """
  26,28,"moose ne kaha"" mashriq o maghrib aur jo kuch un ke darmain hai sab ka rab, agar aap log kuch aqal rakhtay hain """
  26,29,"firaon ne kaha"" agar to ne mere siwa kisi aur ko mabood banaya to tujhe mein unn logon mein shaamil kar dun ga jo qaid khaanoon mein parre sarr rahay hain """
  26,30,"moose ne kaha"" agarchay mein le aon tairay samnay aik Sarih cheez bhi? """
  26,31,"firaon ne kaha"" acha to le aa agar to sacha hai """
  26,32,( is ki zabaan se yeh baat nikaltay hi ) moose ne apna asa phenka aur yakayak woh aik Sarih asdeha tha
  26,33,phir uss ne apna haath ( baghal se ) khincha aur woh sab dekhnay walon ke samnay chamak raha tha
  26,34,"firaon apne gird o paish ke sardaro se bola"" yeh shakhs yaqeenan aik maahir jadugar hai"
  26,35,"chahta hai ke apne jaadoo ke zor se tum ko malik se nikaal day ab batao tum kya hukum dete ho? """
  26,36,"unhon ne kaha"" usay aur is ke bhai ko rok lijiye aur shehron mein hrkare bhaij degiye"
  26,37,"ke har syane jadugar ko aap ke paas le ayen """
  26,38,chunancha aik roz muqarrar waqt par jadugar ikathay kar liye gay
  26,39,"aur logon se kaha gaya"" tum ijtima mein chalo ge ?"
  26,40,"shayad ke humjadogaron ke deen hi par reh jayen agar woh ghalib rahay """
  26,41,"jab jadugar maidan mein aa gay to unhon ne firaon se kaha"" hamein inaam to miley ga agar hum ghalib rahay? """
  26,42,"is ne kaha"" haan, aur tum to is waqtmuqarabain mein shaamil ho jao ge """
  26,43,"moose ne kaha"" phenko jo tumhe phenkna hai """
  26,44,"unhon ne foran apni rasiyaan aur lathyan pheink den aur bolay"" firaon ke Iqbal se hum hi ghalib rahen ge """
  26,45,phir moose ne apna asa phenka to yakayak woh un ke jhutay karishmo ko harap karta chala ja raha tha
  26,46,is par saaray jadugar be ikhtiyar sjday mein gir parre
  26,47,"aur bol utthay ke"" maan gay hum rab alameen ko"
  26,48,"moose aur haroon ke rab ko """
  26,49,"firaon ne kaha"" tum moose ki baat maan gay qabal is ke ke mein tumhe ijazat deta! zaroor yeh tumhara bara hai jis ne tumhe jaadoo sikhaya hai acha, abhi tumhe maloom howa jata hai, mein tumahray haath paon mukhalif simtao mein کٹواﺅں ga aur tum sab ko suli charha dun ga """
  26,50,"unhon ne jawab diya"" kuch parwah nahi, hum apne rab ke huzoor poanch jayen ge"
  26,51,"aur hamein tawaqqa hai ke hamara rab hamaray gunah maaf kar day ga kyunkay sab se pehlay hum imaan laaye hain """
  26,52,"hum ne moose ko wahi bhaije ke"" raton raat mere bundon ko le kar nikal jao, tumhara peecha kya jaye ga """
  26,53,is par firaon ne ( faujein jama karne ke liye ) shehron mein naqeeb bhaij diye
  26,54,"( aur kehla bheja ) ke"" yeh kuch muthi bhar log hain"
  26,55,aur unhon ne hum ko bohat naraaz kya hai
  26,56,"aur hum aik aisi jamaat hain jis ka Shewa har waqt chokanna rehna hai """
  26,57,iss terhan hum inhen un ke baghoon aur chashmon
  26,58,aur khazanon aur un ki behtareen qiyam gaahon se nikaal laaye
  26,59,"yeh to howa unn ke sath, aur ( doosri taraf ) bani Israel ko hum ne un sab cheezon ka waris kar diya"
  26,60,subah hotay hi yeh log unn ke taqub mein chal parre
  26,61,"jab dono garohoon ka aamna saamna howa to moose ke saathi cheekh utthay ke"" hum to pakdae gay """
  26,62,"moose ne kaha"" hargiz nahi mere sath mera rab hai woh zaroor meri rahnumai farmaiye ga """
  26,63,"hum ne moose ko wahi ke zareya se hukum diya ke"" maar apna asa samandar par"" yakayak samandar phatt gaya aur is ka har tukda aik azeem al shan pahar ki terhan ho gaya"
  26,64,usi jagah hum dosray giroh ko bhi qareeb le aeye
  26,65,"moose aur unn sab logon ko jo is ke sath thay, hum ne bacha liya"
  26,66,aur dosaron ko ghark kar diya
  26,67,"is waqea mein aik nishani hai, magar inn logon mein se aksar maan-ne walay nahi hain"
  26,68,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
  26,69,aur aِnhin ibrahim ka qissa sunaaoo
  26,70,"jabkay is ne apne baap aur apni qoum se poocha tha ke"" yeh kya cheeze hain jin ko tum pujte ho? """
  26,71,"unhon ne jawab diya"" kuch buut hain jin ki hum pooja karte hain aur unhi ki siwa mein hum lagey rehtay hain """
  26,72,"is ne poocha"" kya yeh tumhari suntay hain jab tum inhen pukarte ho ?"
  26,73,"ya yeh tumhe kuch naffa ya nuqsaan pohanchate hain? """
  26,74,"unhon ne jawab diya"" nahi, balkay hum ne apne baap dada ko aisa hi karte paaya hai """
  26,75,"is par ibrahim ne kaha"" kabhi tum ne ( ankhen khol kar ) unn cheezon ko dekha bhi jin ki bandagi tum"
  26,76,aur tumahray pichlle baap dada baja laatay rahay ?
  26,77,"mere to yeh sab dushman hain, bajuz aik rab alameen ke"
  26,78,"jis ne mujhe peda kya, phir wohi meri rahnumai farmata hai"
  26,79,jo mujhe khelata aur plata hai
  26,80,aur jab mein bemaar ho jata hon to wohi mujhe Shifa deta hai
  26,81,jo mujhe mout day ga aur phir dobarah mujh ko zindagi bakhshay ga
  26,82,"aur jis se mein umeed rakhta hon ke rozِ jaza mein woh meri khata maaf farma day ga """
  26,83,"( iss ke baad ibrahim ne dua ki )"" ae mere rab, mujhe hukum ataa kar aur mujh ko salhon (saleh logon)ke sath mila"
  26,84,aur baad ke anay walon mein mujh ko sachhi namwari ataa kar
  26,85,aur mujhe janat-e Naeem ke varson mein shaamil farma
  26,86,aur mere baap ko maaf kar day ke be shak woh gumraah logon mein se hai
  26,87,aur mujhe is din ruswa nah kar jabkay sab log zindah kar ke uthaye jayen ge
  26,88,jabkay nah maal koi faida day ga nah aulaad
  26,89,"bajuz is ke ke koi shakhs qalb Saleem liye hue Allah ke huzoor haazir ho """
  26,90,( is roz ) jannat parhaiz garon ke qareeb le aayi jaye gi
  26,91,aur dozakh behke hue logon ke samnay khol di jaye gi
  26,92,"aur un se poocha jaye ga ke"" ab kahan hain woh jin ki tum khuda ko chore kar ibadat kya karte thay ?"
  26,93,"kya woh tumhari kuch madad kar rahay hain ya khud apna bachao kar satke hain? """
  26,94,phir woh mabood aur yeh behke hue log
  26,95,aur iblees ke lashkar sab ke sab is mein ooper taley dhakel diye jayen ge
  26,96,wahan yeh sab aapas mein jhagrain ge aur yeh behke hue log ( apne mabodon se ) kahin ge
  26,97,"ke"" khuda ki qasam, hum to Sarih gumraahi mein mubtala thay"
  26,98,jabkay tum ko rab alameen ki barabari ka darja day rahay thay
  26,99,aur woh mujrim log hi thay jinhon ne hum ko is gumraahi mein dala
  26,100,ab nah hamara koi sfarshi hai
  26,101,aur nah koi jigaree dost
  26,102,"kash hamein aik dafaa phir palatnay ka mauqa mil jaye to hum momin hon """
  26,103,"yaqeenan is mein aik barri nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar log imaan laane walay nahi"
  26,104,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
  26,105,qoum Nooh ne Rasolo-n ko jhatlaya
  26,106,"yaad karo jabkay un ke bhai Nooh ne un se kaha tha"" kya tum drtay nahi ho ?"
  26,107,mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon
  26,108,lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,109,mein is kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon mera ajar to rab alameen ke zimma hai
  26,110,"pas tum Allah se daro aur ( be-khatkay) meri itaat karo """
  26,111,"unhon ne jawab diya"" “kiya hum tujhe maan lein halaank teri pairwi razeel tareen logon ne ikhtiyar ki hai? """
  26,112,"Nooh ne kaha"" mein kya jaanun ke un ke amal kaisay hain"
  26,113,"un ka hisaab to mere rab ke zimma hai, kash tum kuch shaoor se kaam lau"
  26,114,mera yeh kaam nahi hai ke jo imaan layein un ko mein dhtkar dun
  26,115,"mein to bas aik saaf saaf mutnabba kar dainay wala aadmi hon """
  26,116,"unhon ne kaha"" ae Nooh, agar to baz nah aaya tu phatkary hu-ay logon mein shaamil ho kar rahay ga """
  26,117,"Nooh ne dua ki"" “aymere rab, meri qoum ne mujhe jhutla diya"
  26,118,"ab mere aur un ke darmain do toak faisla kar day aur mujhe aur jo momin mere sath hain un ko nijaat day """
  26,119,aakhir kaar hum ne is ko aur is ke sathiyon ko aik bhari hui kashti mein bacha liya
  26,120,aur is ke baad baqi logon ko ghark kar diya
  26,121,"yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar log maan-ne walay nahi"
  26,122,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
  26,123,Aad ne Rasolo-n ko jhatlaya
  26,124,"yaad karo jabkay un ke bhai hood ne un se kaha tha"" kya tum drtay nahi ?"
  26,125,mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon
  26,126,lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,127,mein is kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon mera ajar to rab alameen ke zimma hai
  26,128,yeh tumhara kya haal hai ke har ounchay maqam par laa haasil aik yadgar imarat bana daaltay ho
  26,129,aur barray barray qasr taamer karte ho goya tumhe hamesha rehna hai
  26,130,aur jab kisi par haath daaltay ho jabbar ban kar daaltay ho
  26,131,pas tum log Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,132,daro uss se jis ne woh kuch tumhe diya hai jo tum jantay ho
  26,133,"tumhe janwar diye, avladin den"
  26,134,baagh diye aur chashmay diye
  26,135,"mujhe tumahray haq mein aik barray din ke azaab ka dar hai """
  26,136,"unhon ne jawab diya"" to nasiyaat kar ya nah kar, hamaray liye yaksaa hai"
  26,137,yeh baatein to yun hi hoti chali aayi hain
  26,138,"aur hum azaab mein mubtala honay walay nahi hain """
  26,139,"aakhir kaar unhon ne ussay jhutla diya aur hum ne un ko halaak kar diya yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar log maan-ne walay nahi hain"
  26,140,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
  26,141,smod ne Rasolo-n ko jhatlaya
  26,142,"yaad karo jabkay un ke bhai saleh ne un se kaha"" kya tum drtay nahi ?"
  26,143,mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon
  26,144,lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,145,"mein is kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi, mera ajar to rab alameen ke zimma hai"
  26,146,"kya tum unn sab cheezon ke darmain, jo yahan hain, bas yun hi itminan se rehne diye jao ge ?"
  26,147,inn baghoon aur chashmon mein ?
  26,148,inn khaiton aur nkhlstanon mein jin ke khoshay ras bharay hain ?
  26,149,tum pahar khoud khoud kar fakharya unn mein emiratein banatay ho
  26,150,Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,151,unn be lagaam logon ki itaat nah karo
  26,152,"jo zameen mein fasaad barpaa karte hain aur koi islaah nahi karte """
  26,153,"unhon ne jawab diya"" to mehez aik sehar zada aadmi hai"
  26,154,"to hum jaisay aik ensaan ke siwa aur kya hai laa koi nishani agar to schcha hai """
  26,155,"saleh ne kaha"" yeh oontni hai aik din is ke peenay ka hai aur aik din tum sab ke pani lainay ka"
  26,156,"is ko hargiz nah chhairna warna aik barray din ka azaab tum ko aa le ga """
  26,157,magar unhon ne is ki kochin kaat den aur aakhir kaar pachhtatey reh gay
  26,158,"azaab ne inhen aa liya yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar maan-ne walay nahi"
  26,159,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
  26,160,loot ki qoum ne Rasolo-n ko jhatlaya
  26,161,"yaad karo jabkay un ke bhai loot ne un se kaha tha"" kya tum drtay nahi ?"
  26,162,mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon
  26,163,lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,164,"mein is kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon, mera ajar to rab alameen ke zimma hai"
  26,165,kya tum duniya ki makhlooq mein se Mardon ke paas jatay ho
  26,166,"aur tumhari biwion mein tumahray rab ne tumahray liye jo kuch peda kya hai usay chore dete ho? balkay tum log to hadd se hi guzar gay ho """
  26,167,"unhon ne kaha “اے loot,"" agar to inn baton se baz nah aaya to jo log hamari bustiyon se nikalay gay hain unn mein to bhi shaamil ho kar rahay ga """
  26,168,"is ne kaha"" tumahray krtoton par jo log کڑھ rahay hain mein unn mein shaamil hon"
  26,169,"ae parvar-digaar, mujhe aur mere ahal o Ayal ko un ki bad kardatyon se nijaat day """
  26,170,aakhir kaar hum ne usay aur is ke sab ahal o Ayal ko bacha liya
  26,171,bajuz aik budiya ke jo peechay reh jaane walon mein thi
  26,172,phir baqi mandah logon ko hum ne tabah kar diya
  26,173,"aur un par brsayi aik barsaat, barri hi burii barish thi jo unn dry jaane walon par nazil hui"
  26,174,"yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar inn mein se aksar maan-ne walay nahi"
  26,175,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
  26,176,ashaab الایکہul aikah ne Rasolo-n ko jhutlaya
  26,177,"yaad karo jabkay Shoiab ne un se kaha tha"" kya tum drtay nahi ?"
  26,178,mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon
  26,179,lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,180,mein is kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon mera ajar to rab alameen ke zimma hai
  26,181,pemanay theek bharo aur kisi ko ghata nah do
  26,182,sahih traazo se tulo
  26,183,aur logon ko un ki cheeze kam nah do zameen mein fasaad nah pheilatay phiro
  26,184,"aur uss zaat ka khauf karo jis ne tumhe aur guzashta naslon ko peda kya hai """
  26,185,"unhon ne kaha"" to mehez aik sehr zadahaadmi hai"
  26,186,"aur to kuch nahi magar aik ensaan hum hi jaissa, aur hum to tujhe bilkul jhoota samajte hain"
  26,187,"agar to sacha hai to hum par aasman ka koi tukda gira day """
  26,188,"Shoiab ne kaha"" mera rab jaanta hai jo kuch tum kar rahay ho """
  26,189,"unhon ne usay jhutla diya, aakhir kaar chhatri walay din ka azaab un par aa gaya, aur woh barray hi khofnaak din ka azaab tha"
  26,190,"yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar log maan-ne walay nahi"
  26,191,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
  26,192,yeh rab alameen ki nazil kardah cheez hai
  26,193,usay le kar tairay dil par amanat daar rooh utri hai
  26,194,taakay to unn logon mein shaamil ho jo ( khuda ki taraf se Khalq khuda ko ) mutnabba karne walay hain
  26,195,saaf saaf arabi zabaan mein
  26,196,aur aglay logon ki kitabon mein bhi yeh mojood hai
  26,197,kya inn ( ehley mecca ) ke liye yeh koi nishani nahi hai ke isay ulama bani Israel jantay hain ?
  26,198,( lekin inn ki hatt dharmi ka haal yeh hai ke ) agar ahem usay kisi ajmi par bhi nazil kar dete
  26,199,aur yeh ( Fasih arabi kalaam ) woh un ko parh kar sunataa tab bhi yeh maan kar nah dete
  26,200,isi terhan hum ne is ( zikar ) ko mujrimon ke dilon mein guzaraa hai
  26,201,woh is par imaan nahi laatay jab taq azaab alim nah dekh len
  26,202,phir jab woh be khaberi mein un par aa parta hai
  26,203,"uss waqt woh kehte hain"" ke “kiya ab hamein kuch mohlat mil sakti hai? """
  26,204,to kya yeh log hamaray azaab ke liye jaldi macha rahay hain ?
  26,205,"tum ne kuch ghhor kya, agar hum inhen barson taq aish karne ki mohlat bhi day den"
  26,206,aur phir wohi cheez un par aa jaye jis se inhen daraya ja raha hai
  26,207,to woh samanِ zeist jo un ko mila howa hai inn ke kis kaam aeye ga ?
  26,208,( dekho ) hum ne kabhi kisi bastii ko iss ke baghair halaak nahi kya ke uss ke liye khabardaar karne walay haq nasiyaat ada karne ko mojood thay
  26,209,aur hum zalim nah thay
  26,210,iss ( kitaab Mubin ) ko shyatin le kar nahi utre hain
  26,211,"nah yeh kaam un ko sajta hai, aur nah woh aisa kar hi satke hain"
  26,212,woh to is ki samaat taq se door rakhay gay hain
  26,213,"pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, Allah ke sath kisi doosray mabood ko nah poukaro, warna tum bhi saza panay walon mein shaamil ho jao ge"
  26,214,apne qareeb tareen rishta daaron ko dra-o
  26,215,aur imaan laane walon mein se jo log tumhari pairwi ikhtiyar karen un ke sath tawaza se paish aao
  26,216,lekin agar woh tumhari nafarmani karen to un se kaho ke jo kuch tum karte ho is se mein buri alz Meh hon
  26,217,aur uss zabardast aur Raheem par tawakkal karo
  26,218,jo tumhe is waqt dekh raha hota hai jab tum uthte ho
  26,219,aur sajda guzaar logon mein tumhari naqal o harkat par nigah rakhta hai
  26,220,woh sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai
  26,221,"logo, kya mein tumhe batau ke shyatin kis par utra karte hain ?"
  26,222,woh har ja-al saaz badkaar par utra karte hain
  26,223,"suni sunai baatein kaanon mein phonkay hain, aur un mein se aksar jhutay hotay hain"
  26,224,"rahay shouraa, to un ke peechay behke hue log chala karte hain"
  26,225,kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke woh har waadi mein bhataktay hain
  26,226,aur aisi baatein kehte hain jo karte nahi
  26,227,"bajuz unn logon ke jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye aur Allah ko kasrat se yaad kya aur jab un par zulm kya gaya to sirf badla le liya, aur zulm karne walon ko anqareeb maloom ho jaye ga ke woh kis injaam se dochar hotay hain"
